{"tid":673783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：阿叔搭西鐵　兩蚊運大樹","createTime":"2018-05-22T06:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T08:37:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8bbcc2b525b93d40324af8438ef9dc0e01100731","tid":673783,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:48:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180522/20398254\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180522%2F20398254&d=l5eGLvVAMMxnCWCHCGEdVJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=fcdbfb02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180522%2F20398254&h=ffcaf1b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180522/20398254</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月22日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：阿叔搭西鐵　兩蚊運大樹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180522/large/a0904a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180522%2Flarge%2Fa0904a.gif&h=6e0fe924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■伯伯攜同近3米高長形植物直入屯門。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年3月一名女學生搭港鐵時，因大提琴琴盒其中一邊尺寸超出規定，喺車廂被職員截停帶到客務中心檢查，激發逾千網民畀嬲，質疑港鐵「大細超」，專恰樂手卻放生水貨客。<br />\n<br />\n網傳一名阿伯疑公然挑戰港鐵行李尺寸規定，攜帶近3米高長形植物進入西鐵車廂，有目擊者話，「南昌已經見到佢喺車上，坐到入屯門」，有網民留言嘲諷「廢老」只須花兩蚊（長者乘車優惠）就可付運大樹，「$2一個人加一件大貨，全世界冇車費咁平！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵回覆話唔清楚有關相片來源同拍攝時間，指日前西鐵綫沿途各站無相關紀錄，亦未有收到乘客反映此事。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：凌晨混戰　大埔FYY盲拳揼肥佬<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：少年自備紙軚盤揸巴士"},{"pid":"d398bb9d0fd056d6ce250760d7d6145f5c5b0d95","tid":673783,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:51:11.000Z","msg":"港鐵回覆話唔清楚有關相片來源同拍攝時間，指日前西鐵綫沿途各站無相關紀錄，亦未有收到乘客反映此事。<br />\n<br />\n張圖P出黎?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f7ba49be302f0e81fbacc69cb8906e1cddb4cd","tid":673783,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:14:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ab58b763723649cfc807d16a180dee599ca1a5d","tid":673783,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d398bb9d0fd056d6ce250760d7d6145f5c5b0d95","tid":673783,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:51:11.000Z","msg":"港鐵回覆話唔清楚有關相片來源同拍攝時間，指日前西鐵綫沿途各站無相關紀錄，亦未有收到乘客反映此事。<br />\n<br />\n張圖P出黎?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:37:29.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士係咁上下。"}]}